      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Google Maps Crawler (SerpAPI)\n\n### What it does:\n1. Searches Google Maps via SerpAPI\n2. Extracts: Name, Address, Phone, Rating, Reviews, Hours, GPS\n3. Saves to Google Sheets\n4. Runs daily at 9 AM automatically\n\n### Setup:\n1. Get SerpAPI key: https://serpapi.com/\n2. Replace YOUR_SERPAPI_KEY in workflow\n3. Create Google Sheet and update ID\n4. Activate!\n\n### Pricing:\n- Free: 100 searches/month\n- Hobby: $50/month (5,000 searches)\n- Much cheaper than Google Maps API!",
